Question
========

Below is a portion of an ANOVA table belonging to an RCB ANOVA.

  -------------- ---- ---- ---- --- Variation source df SS MS F Treatment 4 48 Block 2 22 Error 8 20 Total 14 90 -------------- ---- ---- ---- ---

In the experiment to which this table refers, how many observations were to which this table refers?

Answerlist
----------

* 5
* 14
* 15
* 28

Solution
========

Answerlist
----------

* 5: Incorrect
* 14: Incorrect
* 15: Correct
* 28: Incorrect
